{"route":{"route":"/posts/1751943e/","outputPath":"posts/1751943e/index.html","kind":"post","title":"DNSSEC","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"1751943e"}},"description":"这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章 DNS EDNS DNSSEC DNS over HTTPS 完整代码请看DNS 注意: 这里我只完成了请求字段,主要原因是因为我学习这些DNS协议是为了找到防止DNS污染的方法,而DNSSEC并不能,而且应答头比较复杂,可能还要了解ssl和tls的知识,所以这里我没有完成代码,想了解","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/DNSSEC.md","route":"/posts/1751943e/","abbrlink":"1751943e","title":"DNSSEC","date":"2020-06-23 00:21:33","updated":"2020-06-23 00:21:33","tags":["DNS","UDP","DNSSEC","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章<br>\n<a href=\"/posts/f05986bf/\">DNS</a>  <a href=\"/posts/668530ca/\">EDNS</a> <a href=\"/posts/1751943e/\">DNSSEC</a> <a href=\"/posts/4b39445f/\">DNS over HTTPS</a> 完整代码请看<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/tree/master/net/dns\">DNS</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>注意: 这里我只完成了请求字段,主要原因是因为我学习这些DNS协议是为了找到防止DNS污染的方法,而DNSSEC并不能,而且应答头比较复杂,可能还要了解ssl和tls的知识,所以这里我没有完成代码,想了解的请看<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3225\">protocol change</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4034\">rfc4034</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4035\">rfc4035</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4034#appendix-A.1\">Algorithm</a></p>\n<p>DNSSEC也是使用了EDNS,而且只需要改一个字段,就是之前提到Z,具体协议请看</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">                +0 (MSB)                +1 (LSB)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">      0: |   EXTENDED-RCODE      |       VERSION         |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">      2: |DO|                    Z                       |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>完成请求头</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">type</span> eDNSHeader <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">struct</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> DnsHeader   []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> Name        [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> Type        [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> PayloadSize [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> ExtendRCode [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> EDNSVersion [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> Z           [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> Data        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">createDNSSEC</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(domain <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>, reqType2 reqType)</span></span> (header eDNSHeader, b []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//eDNSHeader := createEDNSReq(domain,reqType2,[]byte{})</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header = eDNSHeader{}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.DnsHeader = creatRequest(domain, reqType2)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.Name[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.Type = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00000000, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00101001}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.PayloadSize = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00010000, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00000000} <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//4096</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.ExtendRCode = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00000000}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.EDNSVersion = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00000000}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> header.Z = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b10000000, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>b00000000} <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Do bit = 1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> header, createEDNSRequ(header)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>是不是很简单,再结合之前的EDNS就能完成完整的请求</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"1751943e","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}